              - Health, Social and Unemployment insurance regulated by Vietnam Labor Law, to be paid from probation time;

              - Annual paid leave (12days);

              - Additional accident and health insurance;

              - Training opportunities (local and abroad);

              - Team building activities: Summer holiday, Year-end party, Sport…

              - Other benefits from trade union…


              HOW TO APPLY:

              Applicants are advised to send profile in English or Vietnamese (CV + Cover letter +Degree) to the following emails: via VietnamWorks with title: Application for Technical & Commercial position, deadline: 21/07/2018.


              *Note: Due to the high volume of applications, only selected candidates will be contacted for interviewing/testing through a formal correspondence via e-mail.


